edu.harvard.hms.dbmi.bd2k.irct.model.query

Class Query

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.harvard.hms.dbmi.bd2k.irct.model.query.Query
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SubQuery

    @Entity
public class Query
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The query class represents any query against any individual or group of resources. A Query can have many subQueries, and clauses (Joins, Selects, Wheres).
    Author:
    Jeremy R. Easton-Marks
